lead_paragraph: Scott Brown and K.J. Choi, both of moderate length off the tee, are tied for the lead at the Farmers Insurance Open at Torrey Pines, where the South Course is the longest all year on the PGA Tour. It helps to hit it straight.

headline.print_headline: Choi, Brown Tied for Lead at Torrey Pines
